\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\n\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\n\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \"Plan migration\" ở đây là migration gì?\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\n\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":477,"output":565,"totalTokens":24430,"cacheRead":22455,"cacheWrite":933,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776226552335,"responseId":"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9","__openclaw":{"id":"6d34c150","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776226484570,"sessionId":"1809bef8-e85f-45f1-bec9-a828745f9877","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34262,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776226484036,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/1809bef8-e85f-45f1-bec9-a828745f9877.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776226562383,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"061524f4","seq":6}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:tele